{"tid":362699,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Mosaic PiXL 矯視 無切口, 無激光, 非入侵性新技術","createTime":"2017-08-17T06:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T17:26:03.000Z","uid":7371,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"128aad00f6c7e99c00a3c7b7ba4c011ddd8b5e3a","tid":362699,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/143947_f0021feb12c334689f56441deaa1bbdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F143947_f0021feb12c334689f56441deaa1bbdf.jpg&h=52d3296b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/143947_6b49a959f5caa3c40d19c8fac1c43904.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F143947_6b49a959f5caa3c40d19c8fac1c43904.jpg&h=419dda10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMosaic PiXL 矯視<br />\n無切口, 無激光, 非入侵性新技術<br />\nNo cut, No Laser, New Non-Invasive Technology<br />\n<br />\n針對近視患者，Mosaic PiXL 矯視全程毋須開刀亦不用住院，原理是利用UVA紫外光線和光敏劑核黃素眼溶液 Riboflavin 對角膜局部進行照射。光敏劑遇上紫外線會產生化學作用，令角膜纖維中的膠原蛋白緊扣在一起，使角膜變得堅韌，同時局部改變角膜孤度，矯正近視。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇落個技術無咁傷害性<br />\n但新技術安全性可唔可靠？<br />\n有冇話要幾多近視散光度數以下或指定條件先適合做？<br />\n收費幾錢？"},{"pid":"ae9509e427a7afff856f3da231e3dd0a2cb64ee6","tid":362699,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:49:03.000Z","msg":"未聽過<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 矯視技術近年發展得好快"},{"pid":"7b3d23a055d01f5db5a75844f146a64ff606b2db","tid":362699,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未聽過<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 矯視技術近年發展得好快</blockquote><br />\n剛剛先係FB見到<br />\n近年係越黎越多唔同技術可以矯視<br />\n感覺上消費者多左選擇<br />\n但最關心都係安全"},{"pid":"cbf0ec129d3ca4517df2456fe36632e72d7daa58","tid":362699,"uid":124114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"聽落即係將原本半o者o里狀